response.original_title: CZW Night Of Infamy X - Ultimatum
response.overview: November 12th, 2011 :: Combat Zone Wrestling presents Night Of Infamy X from the Asylum Arena in Philadelphia, PA, USA. Matches include:  • Aaron McCormick vs. Uhaa Nation  • Greg Excellent vs. Mia Yim  • Danny Havoc & tHURTeen vs. Campaign For A Better Combat Zone (Drew Gulak & Nui Tofiga)  • CZW Junior Heavyweight Title #1 Contendership Tournament Final Match Ryan McBride vs. AR Fox  • CZW Tag Team Title Match Philly's Most Wanted (BLK Jeez & Joker) (c) vs. Azrieal & Bandido Jr.  • The Runaways (Joe Gacy & Ryan Slater) & Alex Payne vs. BLK OUT (Alex Colon, Rich Swann & Ruckus)  • CZW World Heavyweight Title Match Devon Moore (c) vs. MASADA  • CZW Junior Heavyweight Title Match Adam Cole (c) vs. Sami Callihan
response.title: CZW Night Of Infamy X - Ultimatum
